  <brief_title>Evaluation of CureXcell® in Treating Chronic Venous Leg Ulcers</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase-3 Prospective, Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability and Efficacy of CureXcell® as an Adjunct to Good Ulcer Care Measures in Treating Chronic Venous Leg Ulcers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
