      <agency>Macrocure Ltd.</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Macrocure Ltd.</source>
  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective is to evaluate the clinical benefit of CureXcell® as adjunct to
      Standard of Care in the treatment of Chronic Venous Leg Ulcers. CureXcell® is a cell based
      therapy, containing activated homologous white blood cells prepared from donated healthy
      whole blood. A total of 252 patients will be randomized to receive either CureXcell® or
      Placebo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
